    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's just something people say to be nice, isn't it? honestly, with my job and how i live, everything is so digital and transactional. if i just... disappeared, if i just stopped being part of the machine, it would probably just be a tiny glitch in someone's spreadsheet. it feels like it would be so much quieter for everyone if i just stopped. wouldn't it?",
